FBIS4-38144 "drnes124_p_94001" FBIS-NES-94-124 Daily Report 28 Jun 1994 SOUTH ASIA Afghanistan Government Seen Making Progress Against Militia Government Seen Making Progress Against Militia Radio Announcement Cites `Victory' LD2606162094 LD2606162094 BFN [Editorial Report] Kabul Radio Afghanistan Network in Dari at 1530 GMT on 26 June carries a one-minute live announcement by the "general command of Kabul City garrison." The announcer says: "It is requested from all the units and companies stationed in Kabul city that they avoid aimless firing and manifest their happiness and the victory of the mojahedin with the shout of God is great."
